data.description: This lovely, one owner home in an established neighborhood is roomy and has a nice flow. It is located on a green belt and features a spacious Kitchen with a breakfast bar, plenty of storage and a walk in pantry.  The home has all new flooring and a new roof. The Kitchen is open to the large Living area with a wood-burning fireplace. The private Master bedroom is roomy and has a walk in closet.   The other 2 bedrooms have a full bath between them and are separate from the Master.  The freeway is close and quickly accessible.  This home is priced to sell and won't last long. Come see for yourself and make this your new home!!
